<memo>#NOTES#<modelview> <source customSQL="select T1.Name as CapabilityName, T2.Name as KPI, T2.Note as Description 
from (t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_connector ON (t_connector.End_Object_ID = T1.Object_ID)) 
LEFT JOIN t_object as T2 ON (t_connector.Start_Object_ID = T2.Object_ID) 
WHERE 
(T1.Object_ID in (Select t_connector.Start_Object_ID FROM t_connector) and
T1.Object_ID in (Select t_connector.End_Object_ID FROM t_connector)) and 
(T1.Stereotype = 'dCapability') AND 
(T2.Stereotype = 'dMeasurementIndicator') AND 
T1.Name in ('Customer Interacting') 
--name of the capability that is linked to KPI's dMeasurementIndicator
ORDER BY T1.Name"/> </modelview>
